text: Pematang Panggang–Kayuagung Toll Road is a toll road that connects Pematang Panggang to Kayuagung in the island of Sumatra, Indonesia.This toll road is part of a network of Trans-Sumatra Toll Road, and is a continuation of the Terbanggi Besar–Pematang Panggang Toll Road and will be connected to the Kayuagung–Palembang–Betung Toll Road. ==Toll gates == {| class="wikitable" !
